QuestData.Title: More Tendrils!
QuestData.CompletionText: You killed many giants, but there are still many more left. And they're still attacking our spore sacs!
QuestData.RewardText: Unbelievable! It would take hundreds of sporelings to slay as many giants as you have. I will make sure to let everyone know of your feats!$B$B<This quest is repeatable up to friendly reputation.>
